OL,3,CWelsh Secretary urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover social media row
OL,6,FThe Welsh Secretary, Jo Stevens, is
OL,7,Fbeing urged to apologise for
OL,8,F'politicising' civil servants in a row
OL,9,Fover the department's social media.
OL,11,FHer Conservative shadow has called for
OL,12,Fthe apology after being told by a
OL,13,Fsenior UK Government official that a
OL,14,Fpost she'd complained about "could
OL,15,Fhave been better phrased."
OL,17,FThe Wales Office says it follows UK
OL,18,FGovernment guidance on the use of
OL,19,Fofficial social media channels.
