OL,6,F"Official accounts must not be used
OL,7,Ffor the further dissemination of
OL,8,Fmessages from party political or
OL,9,Fotherwise partisan accounts. They must
OL,10,Falso be sensitive to tone and guard
OL,11,Fagainst perceived attacks on
OL,12,Fparticular interests, organisations or
OL,13,Findividuals.
