OL,3,CWelsh Secretary urged to apologise
OL,4,Cover social media row
OL,6,F"My team provides comprehensive and
OL,7,Fmandatory training for Government
OL,8,Fcommunications professionals to ensure
OL,9,Fthat these rules are understood. We
OL,10,Falso regularly reinforce the
OL,11,Fobligations through bespoke sessions
OL,12,Fwith Directors of Communication and
OL,13,Ftheir teams.
OL,15,F"In this particular case, while the
OL,16,Ftext of the post echoed a short
OL,17,Fsection of an HM Treasury press
OL,18,Frelease, I acknowledge that it could
OL,19,Fhave been better phrased, and I have
OL,20,Fdiscussed the matter with the Wales
OL,21,FOffice."
