OL,6,FMims Davies said, "I welcome the
OL,7,FDirector General of UK Government
OL,8,FCommunication's response to my letter
OL,9,Fhighlighting, what I believed to be,
OL,10,Fan overtly political post used with
OL,11,Fcivil service resources on the Wales
OL,12,FOffice departmental social media
OL,13,Faccount following the Labour Budget.
OL,14,FHe has agreed in his reply it "could
OL,15,Fhave been better phrased" and has
OL,16,F"spoken" with the Wales Office.
